        It is important that you read all of the terms and conditions within this Gig Agreement (Agreement) to ensure that the Vocalist and 
            Producer understand the agreement between Vocalizr, Vocalist and Producer. Once this Agreement is
            agreed to, the Vocalist and Producer are deemed to have read and understood all of the terms and conditions and
            any related requirements. This Agreement may limit the Vocalist’s and/or Producer’s rights. If the Vocalist or Producer 
            does not understand and/or accept all of the terms and conditions in this Agreement, please do not sign. This Contract governs the
            relationship between Vocalizr, Vocalist and Producer.
    </div>
    
