        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">5.1.</td>
            <td>As from the date of signing this Agreement and subject to the Agreement terms and conditions, you agree to share vocals, production, lyrics,
                song writing and top line in accordance with the collaboration posting.  Gig requirements (Assets) listed by the Employer in the Gig,
                and of a quality that is acceptable to the Employer for the Gig to which this Agreement applies. The Employer will determine 
                whether the Assets offered are accepted. Once the Assets are accepted the required payments as specified in clause
                10 below will be finalised.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">5.2.</td>
            <td>If the Assets are not delivered to the Employer by the Employee, this Agreement becomes null and void.</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <p>As from the date of signing of this agreement and subject to the agreement terms and conditions the Vocalist agrees 
        to offer vocals in the form and quality that is acceptable to the Producer. 
        The Producer will determine whether the vocals offered are accepted. Once accepted,
        the Producer will release the payment, the amount of which is specified in this agreement, to the Vocalist and Vocalizr.</p>
    
