    <p>If the Vocalizr PayPal account - <a href="mailto:payments@vocalizr.com">payments@vocalizr.com</a> <strong>(Payment Service)</strong> is used, then the Vocalist and Producer
        using the Payment Service agree that upon the Producer’s release of payment, the Vocalist automatically transfers
        and assigns to the Producer all rights, title and interest, absolutely, to the copyright and other intellectual property
        in or relating to the music, free of all licences, mortgages, charges or other encumbrances, unless agreed otherwise by the parties 
        in writing. To avoid any doubt, the Vocalist, unless there is an agreement in writing, will not have rights to any royalties associated with
        the use of the vocals in any music. </p>
    
    <h4>7. TERRITORY</h4>
    <p>This agreement applies throughout the world in all countries and territories.</p>

    <h4>8. TERM</h4>
    <p>This Agreement will commence once it is signed by the Producer. 
        The Vocalist is deemed to have accepted this Agreement by reviewing and accepting these terms and conditions prior to offering a bid on the Gig. The timeframe for the use of the vocals is not time limited unless a separate agreement is entered into following this Agreement.</p>
    
    <h4>9. FORMAT</h4>
    <p>This agreement covers all formats, physical and non-physical. Physical formats include, but are not limited to, CD and/or vinyl record 
        and non-physical formats include, but are not limited to, digital downloads/ringtones.</p>
    
