    <table class="decimal-list" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">10.1.</td>
            <td>Payments are only to be made through the Vocalizr Payment Service. The Vocalist and Producer agree not to circumvent Vocalizr’s Payment Service by (but not limited to): soliciting work with Vocalizr members outside the Vocalizr website, accepting work with Vocalizr members outside the Vocalizr website, receiving payment outside the Payment Service, altering Gig Payment amounts after the date of this Agreement, manipulating the Gig bidding process to impact the Gig Payment amounts. </td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">10.2.</td>
            <td>If the Vocalizr Payment Service is circumvented by (but not limited to): soliciting work with Vocalizr members outside the Vocalizr website, accepting work with Vocalizr members outside the Vocalizr website, receiving payment outside the Payment Service, altering Gig Payment amounts after the date of this Agreement, manipulating the Gig bidding process to impact the Gig Payment amounts, this Agreement will immediately become null and void. </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="num">10.3.</td>
            <td>The Producer has agreed that 
                {% if projectBid is defined %}
                <strong>USD ${{ (projectBid.amount / 100)|number_format(2) }} (Gig Payment)</strong>
                {% else %}
                USD $&lt;&lt; INSERT THE TOTAL GIG AMOUNT &gt;&gt; <strong>(Gig Payment)</strong>
                {% endif %}
            will be placed into payment protection immediately.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">10.4.</td>
            <td>The Producer has agreed that once a bid is awarded to the Vocalist, the Producer will pay Vocalizr {% if projectBid is defined %}<strong>USD ${{ (projectBid.amount|getPricePercent(subscriptionPlan.project_percent_added) / 100)|number_format(2) }}</strong>{% else %}USD $&lt;&lt; VOCALIZR PORTION OF PAYMENT &gt;&gt;{% endif %}.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">10.5.</td>
            <td>
                The Producer has agreed that once the vocals offered by the Vocalist have been accepted, the Vocalist will be paid 
                {% if projectBid is defined %}
                <strong>USD ${{ (projectBid.amount / 100)|number_format(2) }}</strong>
                {% else %}
                USD $&lt;&lt; VOCALIST PORTION OF PAYMENT &gt;&gt;
                {% endif %}.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">10.6.</td>
            <td>
                The Vocalist has agreed that they will pay Vocalizr 
                {% if projectBid is defined %}
                <strong>USD ${{ (projectBid.amount|getPricePercent(subscriptionPlan.payment_percent_taken) / 100)|number_format(2) }}</strong>
                {% else %}
                USD $&lt;&lt; INSERT VOCALIST PAYMENT AMOUNT TO VOCALIZR &gt;&gt;
                {% endif %}. This will be deducted from the amount paid to the Vocalist by the Producer.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">10.7.</td>
            <td>The Employer and Employee have agreed that a mechanical royalty of <strong>{% if project is defined and project.royaltyMechanical %}{{ project.royalty }}{% else %}0{% endif %}%</strong> is payable to the Employee for the Assets
                provided in the Gig to which this Agreement applies.</td>
        </tr> 
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">10.8.</td>
            <td>The Employer and Employee have agreed that a performance royalty of <strong>{% if project is defined and project.royaltyPerformance %}{{ project.royalty }}{% else %}0{% endif %}%</strong> is payable to the Employee for the Assets provided 
                in the Gig to which this Agreement applies.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">10.9.</td>
            <td>Where there is a royalty of '0%' this means that the mechanical and/or performance royalty has no value assigned.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">10.10.</td>
            <td>If a royalty percentage has been agreed to, it is the responsibility of the Employer and Employee to register their interest
                with the royalty association of the country in which they reside. Vocalizr will not bear any responsibility for this. </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
